Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,Ugw0UHFLeo5kPps5KGx4AaABAg,,@fast_richard,"The time setting of the movie is about a year and a half after the Germans rolled into Paris, a few days before the Japanese attack on Pearl Harbor triggering the American abandonment of neutrality and entry into the war.  The movie can be looked at as an allegory of America, represented by Rick Blaine, joining the fight.",2026-05-01T19:48:23Z,2026-05-01T19:48:23Z,2,False,0.0,2026-05-02T02:01:02.698180
