Tangier,wJhvcmFMpwY,UgyouqjgOn8LVa_NLf14AaABAg.9WpqZRpKOKLA76E4LZ21MX,UgyouqjgOn8LVa_NLf14AaABAg,@duffgordon9005,"Tangier was THE PICK of ATCO RECORDS (CREME) for that great label (on hiatus) to be 'reborn' . They hired Andy Johns as Producer - did the MTV films.. put a lot of $$ into them.and promotion. They toured with Cinderalla , 38 Special-- If you go to Amazon and put in their LP's , you will read, from HARD CORE ROCKERS.. 5 star after 5 star, and even Anger- ""how come I never knew about these guys""!!  The problem imo was 3-fold. 1) It was the end of the glammish rockers, and the opposite came flooding in- KURT COBAIN and the like 2)  The key to the staying power is ""a HIT""  if not number having a number one- All their soings are ""hittable"" but it just did not happen. I always say, play ALL three LP's and chances are you will not sigh and ""skip songs here and there. "" Doug Gordon, started playing guitar at 16, and got signed at 28- supplying dozens of songs, and was featured in Guitar PLayer. He always said, I am either going to make it, and continue on, or ""that's that"" It's a testament that their music has not aged.I love the Remastering of 4-winds, . my suprise is not a single Movie, Commercial ever got picked out say ""FEVER for GOLD "" on one of these many mining shows..",2024-08-14T04:05:19Z,2024-08-14T04:05:19Z,2,True,,2026-05-02T02:02:10.142815
