Tangier,wJhvcmFMpwY,UgzbYNj9p9pLY4XXxi94AaABAg.95N0hoQ2JXB97OQZp_zc5A,UgzbYNj9p9pLY4XXxi94AaABAg,@davidkersey8059,"Went through several copies of both of those.  Just incredible music for the time.  I discovered them at NRM on a demo disc they were playing in store back in '89?.  Herd both and immediately bought them.  Best choice I ever made.  Still listen to them in the Jeep in the summer with the top off, stereo cranked up, and the wind just blowing in my face.  Thank god for cd burners and MP3 files now a days .  I Can have a copy anytime i need it.",2020-04-13T12:11:34Z,2020-04-13T12:11:34Z,5,True,,2026-05-02T02:02:11.061612
