AFCON,8NFTgffGOqA,UgzINcW_5X3jpu08xtF4AaABAg,,@R.Slawialaoui144tsw,"The Truth About the Towels – AFCON 2026
Rumors suggested that a team intended to create chaos. The refusal by certain players to use the towels provided by CAF—particularly the goalkeepers of Nigeria and Senegal, with the latter insisting on using a blue towel, as the whole world saw—raised suspicions that these towels might contain hidden compartments. In addition, the fact that players’ bags were not checked in the same way as spectators’ bags triggered serious security concerns.
There were also reports that some spectators intended to target Achraf Hakimi following his African Ballon d’Or win.
We were not paranoid—we were responsible. Events later confirmed these rumors in the eyes of the entire world.
Seek the truth before blindly following propaganda fueled by jealousy toward Morocco. Honesty and morality define true humanity.",2026-01-25T08:12:36Z,2026-01-25T08:12:36Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-02T02:02:46.752457
